data.description: Come see this two-year-old condo boasting three bedrooms and 2.5 baths in Glenn Dale Commons!  Home feels like a townhouse with a modern twist.  The main level features luxury vinyl plank flooring and houses a spacious gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an expansive 16' island. Large pantry and plenty of cabinet space to accommodate all your cooking needs. The living area is adorned with coffered ceilings, lending an extra touch of refined elegance. Step outside to enjoy some fresh air on the back deck. Three spacious bedrooms located on the upper level along with the washer/dryer making laundry day easy! Your primary bedroom serves as a true retreat, featuring an extra-large walk-in closet and double vanities in the en-suite bathroom.  Convenience meets functionality in the attached one-car garage and a driveway. Community features a tot lot, gazebo, dog park, and a butterfly garden. Located near major highways (495, 295), this residence ensures easy commuting and access to amenities like plenty of shopping, parks, restaurants and more!
